ABSTRACT : We present a scalable, rational cryptocurrency. Haket provides all the advantages expected of a reliable distributed, cryptographically secured and verified append-only ledger for transactions, with the added benefits of rational value and disincentive towards speculation and arbitrage. Because the value of the Haket is indexed directly and dynamically to the amount of computational work which must be done to verify each block, its value will not fluctuate erratically, and therefore, unlike most other cryptocurrencies, can serve as a money for cases where a reliable unit of value exchange is required.\'a0 Haket is designed as a fully distributed system using the e2e principle that all participants of the system should contribute more computational resources to the system than they use.\'a0\
\
